category: Publishing Python
requires: cygwin libkpathsea4 python tetex
sdesc: "Python TeTeX modules"
ldesc: "PyX is a Python package for the creation of encapsulated 
PostScript figures. It provides both an abstraction of PostScript and a 
TeX/LaTeX interface. Complex tasks like 2d and 3d plots in 
publication-ready quality are built out of these primitives."
